{"about_the_game":"Mirrored Soul is a monster-collecting RPG where no two monsters are alike.<br><br>Part noir, part fantasy, and part buddy comedy, Mirrored Soul takes heavily after the JRPGs of old. The story stars out-of-practice detective Cecel and his mysterious feline sidekick Spot, named for his single, unblinking eye. Traverse dimensions, recruit monsters or shake 'em down for information, take down the armies of the shadowy Mirrorlord  -- and maybe do some sleuthing here and there. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 200 monsters to recruit to your party, each with their own unique way to be recruited (22 recruitable in the demo)!<br></li><li>Challenging, engaging gameplay which requires strategy and teambuilding.<br></li><li>A &quot;monster fusion&quot; mechanic in which players can combine two of their creatures into a new one which inherits skills from each of their movesets.<br></li><li>A pretty banging OST.<br></li><li>Many secrets to find off of the beaten path, from rare monsters to sidequests to bosses. Perhaps there's even something a bit more sinister lying deep within the mirror world...</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886210/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735584838","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886210/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735584838","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886210/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735584838","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886210/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735584838","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Strong language, Mention of alcohol"},"demos":[{"appid":1888250,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"Mirrored Soul is a monster-collecting RPG where no two monsters are alike.<br><br>Part noir, part fantasy, and part buddy comedy, Mirrored Soul takes 